original_title: Australian politician Jason Peter Wood MP who served as the Assistant Minister for Customs
original_body_lines: Australian politician Jason Peter Wood MP who served as the Assistant Minister for Customs, Community Safety and Multicultural Affairs from May 2019 until May 2022 visited the BOI last Friday for a briefing on the investment climate, opportunities in the energy sector, minerals and renewable energy sectors and to
